title: Toyota’s New Prius Gets Sportier Look
text:
Toyota Motor Corp. is giving its pioneering Prius hybrid vehicle a face-lift, betting that a sportier profile and less exhaust emissions will give the car more appeal to American buyers who have lost some of their interest in fuel economy.
